97.1% of IA job creators are small businesses - the economic engine of IA. The Tax Cuts & Jobs Act means their lowest tax rate since WWII
Sorry Kedron - no Oprah car giveaways in this bill. But the Tax Cuts & Jobs Act helps hardworking Iowa families keep more of what they earn
The Tax Cuts & Jobs Act ends the expensive & time-consuming nightmare of tax-filing season so the majority of Iowans will file on a postcardpic.twitter.com/6MEbenAJkp
Under the Tax Cuts & Jobs Act hardworking Iowans will have help with rising costs of child care, higher ed & caring for loved ones. #TaxCuts
Under the Tax Cuts & Jobs Act hardworking Iowans will be able to keep more of their hard-earned money each month. #TaxCuts
Single mother making $30,00 a year will see $700 bigger refund under the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act. #TaxCuts
Family of 4 making $59,000 a year will see $1,182 tax savings under the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act. #TaxCuts #IA03
Protects American jobs from moving overseas by eliminating incentives that now reward companies for shifting jobs & manufacturing abroad.
Reduces business income tax rate on Iowa main street job creators to no more than 25% - lowest rate on small business since WWII
Popular retirement savings options like 401ks & IRAs are retained so Iowans can save for their futures
The tax bill preserves the home mortgage interest tax relief deduction for existing mortgages & for newly purchased homes up to $500,000
The bill continues the tax deduction for charitable contributions so people can continue to donate to their churches and charities.
New family tax credit expands the Child Tax Credit from $1,000 to $1,600 to help parents with the costs of raising children
This bill significantly increases the standard tax deduction from $6,350 to $12,700 for individuals & $12,700 to $24,000 for married couples
Tax Cuts & Jobs Act lowers tax rates for low & middle income Iowans so people can keep more of the money they earn throughout their lives.
Tax relief will help hardworking Iowans who have been struggling to finally get ahead rather than just getting by. #TaxCuts
The Tax Cuts & Jobs Act is a bold pro-growth bill which will give a typical hardworking middle-income family a $1,182 #taxcut #IA03
